---
import AppLayout from "../layouts/AppLayout.astro";
import UkPhoneNumberGenerator from "../components/UkPhoneNumberGenerator";
---

<AppLayout title="Help" description="Help using your clubcard barcode.">
  <script is:inline>
    try {
      localStorage.setItem("lastCheckedHelp", Date.now().toString());
    } catch {
      // The help page still works when browser storage is unavailable.
    }
  </script>

  <section class="screen" aria-labelledby="help-title">
    <header class="header">
      <div class="title-row">
        <h1 id="help-title">Appless Tesc* UK</h1>
        <a class="card-link" href="/" aria-label="View your clubcard">
          <span class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <img class="logo" src="/logo.jpg" alt="" width="512" height="512" />
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>No more app!</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>Enter your clubcard number.</li>
          <li>Scan the barcode at the till to collect clubcard points and get member-only discounts.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>
          Your clubcard number stays in your browser and is not sent anywhere.
        </p>

        <a class="button" href="/">Open clubcard barcode</a>
      </article>
      <br />
      <article class="card">
        <h2>How do I get a new clubcard?</h2>
        <ol>
          <li>
            Visit <a
              href="https://www.tesco.com/account/register/en-GB/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">tesco.com/account/register/en-GB/</a
            > to get started. Fill in a real email address that you can access.
          </li>
          <li>
            Enter the required information on the page. You do not need a valid
            UK (+44) phone number. If you don't have one, just make up one.

            <UkPhoneNumberGenerator client:only="react" />
          </li>
          <li>
            You can also enter any address. If you don't have a postal address,
            you can use any or mine at "Winfield House, Outer Circle, Regents
            Park, London, NW1 4RT".
          </li>
          <li>
            You'll receive an email with your clubcard number. Copy it and paste
            into the card number field.
          </li>
        </ol>
      </article>
      <br />
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Why do I need this?</h2>
        <p>
          Tesc* doesn't allow you to view your clubcard barcode directly on
          their website. The till does not allow you to enter your phone number
          or clubcard number to take advantage of their discounts. You also
          cannot download the app unless you have your app store location set to
          United Kingdom.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may also dislike using their app. This website is a lightweight
          alternative that works on any modern mobile browser and allows you to
          view your clubcard barcode without needing to use the official app or
          website.
        </p>
      </article>
      <br />
      <article class="card">
        <h2>Why did you make this?</h2>
        <p>
          Visitors need to switch to the United Kingdom app store region to
          download the official app. This can be a hassle.
        </p>
        <p>
          Additionally, this demonstrates you do not need a valid local phone
          number or address to register for a clubcard.
        </p>
        <p>
          As of June 2026, this page still works as expected, but Tesc* may
          update their policies to change registration or update barcode
          formats. Enjoy while it lasts!
        </p>
        <p>
          Source code is available on <a
            href="https://github.com/angushtlam/appless-tesco-uk"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            GitHub</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          Want to contact me? Message me on <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/angustofar"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a
          > or <a
            href="https://www.tiktok.com/@angustofar"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">TikTok</a
          >.
        </p>
        <p>
          ©️ Angus Lam 2026. Find my other projects on <a
            href="https://anguslam.com"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer">anguslam.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .screen {
      min-height: inherit;
      color: #fff;
      background: #0057a6;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .title-row {
      position: relative;
      display: grid;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 88px;
      place-items: center;
      padding: max(18px, env(safe-area-inset-top)) 64px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(255 255 255 / 12%);
    }

    .logo {
      display: block;
      width: 96px;
      height: 96px;
      margin: 22px 0;
      border-radius: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .card-link {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: 22px;
      display: grid;
      width: 32px;
      height: 26px;
      place-items: center;
      color: inherit;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .card-icon {
      position: relative;
      display: block;
      width: 28px;
      height: 20px;
      border: 2px solid currentColor;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    .card-icon::before {
      position: absolute;
      top: 4px;
      right: 3px;
      left: 3px;
      height: 3px;
      background: currentColor;
      content: "";
    }

    .content {
      padding: 18px max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-right))
        max(28px, env(safe-area-inset-bottom))
        max(16px, env(safe-area-inset-left));
    }

    .card {
      padding: clamp(28px, 8vw, 42px) 24px 28px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      color: #2d2d2d;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .card h2 {
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      font-size: 1.55rem;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .card ol {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 24px;
      color: #555;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .button {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #fff;
      background: #0057a6;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</AppLayout>
